1. Crawl pages with Google IP
Assume we are detecting cloaking for search in English.
Use Google translate, set original language French and set target language to
English. Paste the link to the search bar. They will retrieve the website on
Google's behalf.

2. Crawl pages with custom IP
PlanetLab. Not available.
Try vpn or 100 midtown ip.

3. Collect abusive words
Money or action related words, think from the attacker point of view
price
sale
download
buy

Collect basic words and then use Google suggest to expand them
Experiment on one category of words first, see how it works

